title: Full House - 2x08 - Triple Date
description:
30. Triple Date 
First aired: 12/9/1988

Writer: Jeff Franklin 
Director: Peter Baldwin 
Guest star: Rebeccah Bush (Denise), Diane Brodie(Cheryl), Jennifer McAllister (Zoey) 



Danny has a hard time trying to find a date that at some point in time Jesse hasn&#039;t dated. Love over broccoli was the plan for Danny until he brings his date home. She brings friends for Joey and Jesse as well. But the best laid plans don&#039;t always work.
